lead_paragraph: Australia's Olympic team leader is keeping the delegation's 700 athletes or staff out of the Athletes Village for at least two days, citing electrical and plumbing problems in the sprawling complex less than two weeks before the start of the games in Rio de Janeiro.

headline.print_headline: Aussies Won't Move to Rio Village Yet; Power, Plumbing Fears
